        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;As a fairly new necro (12), I'm interested in how everyone has their hot banks/buttons set up.<br><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;I recently started duoing with a wizard mate of mine so I've made the various "%T is feared", "%T is snared", etc. buttons. But in doing that, I've had to push over some of my pet command buttons to another bank.<br><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;With a rogue as my main, I'm no stranger to juggling hotkeys. Though (obviously) playing my necro is a whole new ball game, so I'd appreciate any feedback to help me get a lil more organized.<br><BR><br><BR>Thanks in advance!<BR><br></font></td>
