        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Page 1 is my main hunting page, the others are scattered like Abillister's, usually serving one purpose or another such as my Travelling page, alternate pages used when grouping, my spell book page (each set of spell book pages hotkeyed), etc.</P><P>Page 1 is set up like this(53rd Necro):</P><P>Solo:<BR>1. Darkness<BR>2. Pet attack<BR>3. Fear<BR>4. BoD<BR>5. Splurt<BR>6. Tap<BR>7. Pet back off<BR>8. Lich or alternate DoT such as Ignite Blood<BR>9. FD<BR>10. Paralyzing Earth</P><P>Grouped (all multiple choices depend on my role)<BR>1. Snare, Covetous Subversion or Pact of Shadow<BR>2. Pet attack or Secondary Assist<BR>3. Screaming Terror or Alternate DD/DoT<BR>4. BoD<BR>5. Splurt, Rapacious Subversion or Corpal Empathy<BR>6. Tap<BR>7. Pet back off or Main Assist<BR>8. Lich, alternate DoT or Para Earth<BR>9. FD<BR>10. Para Earth or Harmshield</P><P>The reason I may mem both Covetous Subversion AND Rap Subv is those rare times when I need to send mana rapidly without regard to efficiency.  You can chain cast those two if you alternate them.</P><P>Loreana Shahnra<BR>Human Heretic of Innoruuk<BR>Tribunal</P><P>'And the Servants of Death wailed loudly and beat their breasts <BR>with their fists and cries of "No More" went unheard,<BR>for the gods cared not but for their gold.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
